social_posts.post_text: 📻 We’ve got a long-distance dedication in the studio today… Many requests to send this one out to the Governor of Tennessee, you forking FORK.
Lil いちご だいふく whisperin pie inspo in my ear. Happy 3.14 Eve to those who celebrate!
@blk.rnbw + @bettyturbo! Oversized collaborative screenprinted poster adventures. Show at Interzone in April. Stay tuned for more!
Petition to remove my consciousness from this human body and just put it in a computer or a very pokey crab 🦀

Okay, okay, we named our babyyy! The show will be called 13 and we hope you’ll come to our reception on 4/15 at Interzone! Gonna have a DJ, a limited edition zine that goes with the show, and some other cool stuff in the mix TBA. 🌸 @bettyturbo + @blk.rnbw 🌺

Neon inks are impossible to photograph and this lil insta crop will not give you the impact of a 26x40 screen print, so consider this your gentle warmup to your face being totally melted. Swipe to turn out the lights!💥 Collab with @blk.rnbw

The balance of creative kitchen time in my life is a lil off right now bc it’s been nothing but neon posters for weeks but boyyyy oh boy am I lookin forward to dinner partying the heck out of this summer. I really need to get some Swedish pearl sugar to make chouquettes. Also maybe I need a secret dessert window on my house and I’ll activate the phone tree when I bake something and Those Who Know can come get some and leave a sugar tribute. Tell me what baking adventures you’ve been up to so I can enjoy the vicarious thrill.

I was worried this picture full of rainbow flowers was going to damage my reputation as a sad goth who hates the sun, but @blk.rnbw reassured me it’s ok to be a Neon Goth and reminded my skin is literally pale enough to glow in the dark here, so nobody should be coming to take my credentials away. Phew! 🖤 26x40 screenprint collab with my guy @blk.rnbw
My face to the projects popping in my inbox this week. An exciting spring so far!
Raise your hand if you’d rather be making out on another planet than whatever you actually have to be doing on a Mondayyy 🪐 26x40 screenprint collab with @blk.rnbw

A few years back I pitched a Darcelle XV mural on a giant sequin wall for a corporate installation but it didn’t get picked up. ✨ Thinking of her and hoping some beautiful tributes start popping up! ✨ Every day’s a good day to commemorate an absolute legend.
We went to outer space so early on, I guess we never really came back… ✨ another 26x40 screenprint of real life from your friends @bettyturbo + @blk.rnbw

Hey thanks @dandywellington and #blackapparelarts for inspiring me to practice drawing more full body portraits! Been a few years since this drawing and I just realized I’ve done a whole year’s worth for a recurring magazine feature. (Feels slightly less triumphant in the days of dwindling print media when a “monthly”magazine is actually only printed quarterly…😅)

I’m not a quick cartoonist or a fancy fashion illustrator but I really like drawing people and clothes!  I think seven year old me tracing Archie Comics to draw new outfits for Betty and Veronica would be pretty pleased with this situation. Got a few fun costume and fashion-related projects on deck for this summer and looking for more! Anyone have a semi-educational topic they’d want to bring to a coloring book collab??

#BlackApparelArts (see also @blackapparelarts) is an initiative created by entertainer and style icon @dandywellington which invites artists to diversify the world of apparel arts illustrations (especially vintage-inspired). Add your own! Check out the YooToob vid on the project to hear more. And allow me to wholeheartedly recommend following + supporting @dandywellington on every possible platform for many varieties of inspiration, education, and joy! 🍦
Another rainy spring morning holding hands and making giant posters. 🌼🌸🌺 @bettyturbo + @blk.rnbw

V happy birthday to my favorite alien @jennifer.e.crawford, thank you for gracing this planet with your radness! Wishing you a most bodacious next year of existence and a triumphant return to the ring this weekend!!!
Thank you for your patience, we are out of office right now, way far out… @bettyturbo + @blk.rnbw mega collab neon facemelt notes from outer space…

This is the 8th poster we’ve hung for the show so far. Will it really be the end of this series? Hmmm… better come to the reception on 4/15 to find out. ✨ @bettyturbo + @blk.rnbw 26x40 screenprint madness not stopping anytime soon ✨
Another Betty Turbo backpage bit for @pomomagazine. Scope it out and get to know Amanda Mailey’s amazing work supporting and connecting Portland’s women in business! @alist_pdx
Made this jacket for the art show but was grumpy about the flower quality and the hot glue burns in the end and didn’t wear it. Now taking nominations for where it should make its debut… 🌸

Another day waking up on this planet and you can see one of us is wondering if any of those giant flowers will dispense our morning coffee and one of us is wondering how many times we can eat at Tacovore in a week before it gets weird…

Come with us now on a journey through time and space… How far into the future do you think we have to get before Rick Steves is doing time travel shows?? Love to stop off in the daisy-covered 90s and tell our teenage selves how great things were going to get.

All the prints from this show have now been posted for your perusal at bettyturbo.com and will be added to blkrnbw.com too any day now!

Just put this pansy on your tongue and say “Keep on travelin,” everything’s going to be fiiine… 🌺 @bettyturbo + @blk.rnbw mega screenprint face-melting flower adventures now available from bettyturbo dot com so join in while we’re still on this planet 🌼
Brunch has flowers on it too. 🌼 Don’t act surprised! 🌼 Pandan coconut rolls for my homies.

This print is the one I’m most inclined to paper a wall with and then make us matching outfits out of to stand in front of the wall. Brady’s ambivalent about matching outfits but maybe this one will convince him. Made from the camellias right outside my studio widow!

The sun is shining! 🌞 Whatchoo need to carry?? Flowers? A whole CSA box worth of vegetables?? Your nunchucks collection??? I’ve got the perfect huge tote for you and you can grab it exclusively from bettyturbo.com! 🍰 Eat ‘em up babieees.🌞
Scootin all my goodies over to the new web shop but only got three of these left! Will Punch & Pie get a makeover for 2023? 🤔🥧💥🥊 New shirt silliness on the horizon, you know he we roll!
So much sun this week, we got to start planning some Gardens Gone Wild action here at Camp Corndog. If only we could bury these prints under the dirt to cultivate giant wild space flowers!
Babe, have I mentioned you really cause some beautiful disturbances in the magnetosphere of my heart? Way to ionize and excite those atmospheric constituents if you know what I mean.

84 heckin degrees here yesterday. 🫠 The planets have spoken: You deserve a treat.🍦Neapolitan! Hey let’s go to Naples… 🍨 P.S. if you are a Taurus and you’d rather have an entire Viennetta as a single-serving treat, it’s totally fine.
Happy “It’s Gonna Be May” from “Not Justin Timberlake’s Hair” to all who celebrate. For extra credit please explain this caption to someone from the 1800s.

Trying to think of beautiful visualization for messy messy data and I’d like to think it’s just a jumble of delicious cereal bits that need to be sorted, but somehow all the purples are labeled lime? Hey why are there nuts and bolts and broken glass in here?
Portrait of me waking up so early to go to the dentist that there were still toads loudly gossiping in the parking lot and then I had to drink my HOME coffee out of a straw.
Tag yourself! These are all the feelings. I don’t make the rules. 🤷🏻
Tropicália tribute to the absolutely iconic Rita Lee. 🌺 1947-2023.

Our brains are still 92% psychedelic flower images. (5% Cowboy Bebop and 3% ramen.) 🌼 I heard if you make a lil shrine with these prints and say nice things to them it helps your real garden grow. 🌼 Give it a try and let us know how it turns out. 🌼
I don’t know why everyone thinks the sun is so cool, he is clearly a VILLAIN, this weather is RUDE, and I might have to become a professional wrestler just to fight him. ❄️🧊💪🏼🧊❄️
Mondayyyy… 🦺 Up and at em! 🚧 And don’t forget to pack a wholesome meal for your union-mandated lunch break!
What is your summer sipping destiny??🥤Crack open a tall cool one if you dare!
I have made four rhubarb upside down cakes since this picture was taken and there is still rhubarb left.
HAPPY PRIDE! 💥 Trans people deserve joy, and cake! 💥 And if you think this is a “controversial statement” then you can take it up with ゴジラ! 💥💥💥💥💥💥💥💥💥💥💥💥💥💥💥💥💥💥💥💥💥

Don’t forget the reason for the season! Trans and GNC people of color led the charge! Keep it going! Protest, speak up, keep fighting. Thank you #marshapjohnson #sylviarivera #stormedelarverie #missmajor!
null
Have a nice dayyyyyyy 🏳️‍🌈
Mothra loves you and I do too!!
Perennial reminder that you’re just right, just as you are. 💎
Shimmy, shake, sparkle, shine, and SLIME! This is your time!!
Byeeeeee see ya never.
Heyyyy I drew some stuff for @moveon’s Pride celebrations and you can get this sticker for freee from MoveOn.org!
Keep on sparklin ✨✨✨
Mood.
Love you, mean it. 🍦
Saturn Devouring His Son. (Don’t Talk To Me Or My Son Ever Again.) Hi new friends! Thanks for checking out my art. Grocery Outlet has Viennetta if you need some.

Some Pride munchies from years past. (Swipe for more!) 🍕 Tell me about other flags you use!! 🍿 It doesn’t have to be like you grow up being called Agnes and can never find souvenir tchotchkes with your name on them, we can always draw more snacks with faces!! 🍭 What would you like to add to the menu?

Speaking of #foodwithfaces, buds, I got somethin hot cookin!! 🍕 It’s top secret for now but expect to see a lot more pizza content in this space… 🍕 I promise it’s cooler than that time a publishing company marketed a pizza cookbook with me listed as a co-author without ever asking/telling me about it and I fielded a lot of confusing congratulations and still never heard from them. 🙄 Anyway! Do you like pizza?! 🍕 It’s pizza time!

Hi from my ice cave where I am checking the weather forecast updates for Saturday about six times a day and recalculating in which items from my closet I might be able to tolerate a bit of chaotic outdoor Pride celebrations that morning with the looming reward promise of watching wrasslin and eating ice cream out of a smol baseball helmet later in the day.

Hi, hello! This is your reminder that joy and delight are your flintstone vitamins and you should be consuming them on the regular! For your health! This doesn’t mean ignore the hard things, and it doesn’t mean toxic positivity, it means we NEED to deliberately expose ourselves to nourishing, positive moments to train our minds and bodies what that FEELS like! This is how we stay strong, so we stay in the fight and keep up the work. Put that good stuff in there!!

Commissioner of Sportzballs called, all ball games are now turning into wrestling, I don’t make the rules 🤷🏻 I tried to get an AI to help me break the news to you about this but they refused on the grounds that it’s an illogical and impractical decision, so I guess the robots don’t know everything, do they? 

Baseball + @pow_pro_wrestling tonight at PK Park! But don’t get it twisted, I’m team @jackandsledge all the way. 🔨🔨
Pride Month may be wrapping up but I don’t want a single one of you to simmer down 🏳️‍🌈
Shoutout to all the p r i c k l y  b i t c h e s
Stay hydrated, buds. It’s hot out there. It’s cool in here. In my brain. You can acquire this artwork from my internet HQ. You know what to do.🥤
I just think a pizza slice and an inky squeegee could fall in love. It’s so good to find someone who really gets you.
The Barbie movie was great but it just didn’t have enough wrestlers in it. Guess I’ll hold tight til @doaprowrestling next weekend… 🌹
This Barbie makes little girls scream like they are losing their dang minds and thatttt is a pretty endearing thing about wrestling. 💖 Love those screaming kids. Give them an extra Pepsi for me.🥤
Good night Pee-Wee.
This Barbie needs a @dunkaroos sponsorship.
Happy MCA Day!
Happy Andy Warhol’s bday. Obvs we will be celebrating by eating ice cream and going to more wrestling.
Just randomly thinking about the lost final series of @glownetflix, WYD? 😭

A couple of recent portraits I did for @pomomagazine Ripping the City series. Chris Yen of @laundrypdx for the summer issue and Elan Hagens of @temptresstruffles for the fall issue. Who will be next??

Hmmm I guess I should tell The Internet we’re doing a show this weekend. Saturday! October 7th! Grass Hut Art Market aka Gamjam!! in the Lloyd Center Mall. I’ve got lots of new stickers, and your first peek at this year’s papier-mâché holiday baubles. Heaps of smartass greeting cards if you’re ready to stock up.  @blk.rnbw will be right next to me with all his rad stuff and an amazing mullet that we cut to be silly but I am unironically pretty into it now. Come see us. 🌈 💀

Let’s goooooo!! Grass Hut Art Market opens at 11 in the Lloyd Center Mall!! You know you always wanted to buy weirdo art in an abandoned Ulta! Hey look all the new ornaments this year have a lil charm so they feel extra fancy and collectible! Order upppp!
Punchy says next edition of Punch & Pie gear coming soon, but for now at least all the new stickers are up on my site! 🥧 💥 🥊

How @blk.rnbw and I have adapted to survive the holiday production season: 1) tattoos don’t count against budget discipline, 2) there’s always time for wrestling outings no matter how crammed our workload is, 3) more coffee. Ok I think we’re gonna make it!  Also we love @willowwrestles. 💜
Me walking into Friday with one million projects going and feeling like a blob of jelly trying to pass as an adult human. 🍒
When life gives you lemons… marry someone who will time travel through all your weird h0rny associations with lemonade 🍋🥤
Halloween is OVER!! No more corndogs! Just kidding. Corndogs all day every day. It’s November. I feel my powers growing. I’m ready to put cranberry sauce on a corndog.

Okay ya ding dongs, the current inventory of ornaments I have so far is all available to you now on bettyturbo dot com. 🍓 I will be making lots more!! But no promises on designs or quantities so order ASAP if you’re horngry for holiday magic. 🍓 A few leftovers from last year crept in too, so snag some butts, baguettes, and Battenbergs which are the last of their kind!

Thanks buds! 🍓 Deviled eggs and peppermints cleared out in no time! 🍓 There WILL be more, stay tuned here for updates on the next drop! 🍓 Also I will for sure be hoarding some for the @craftywonderland holiday sale, and I will have a special mall themed ornament release for the @mallratspdx show 12/16! 🍓 Fresh pile of spooky strawberries to keep you company in the meantime!

Just cleaning up the studio here at Betty Turbo World Headquarters to make more room for papier-mâché and it turns out I still have some of these stuffed groceries ornaments from a few years back! Now up on bettyturbo dot com and so is the original poster version! The screenprint elves tell me t-shirts are coming soon…
Dusty is helping me make more Choco Tacos and Topo Chicos today!
Hey look! 🍄 Some wild mushroom ornaments have sprouted up at bettyturbo dot com!
Santa said it was ok to eat these but that boy is into some freaky stuff, maybe we just hang em on the old Yule tree and call it good… 🍄 bettyturbo dot com et cetera and so on what have you
Wake up wake up!! 📺 Fresh ornaments at noon (PST) on bettyturbo dot com!
Only five desserts for ten people is me showing restraint. 🍰 But don’t hold back, grab one of these shirts, maybe one for everyone you know!
Punch and Pie rides again!! 🥧💥🥊 Have some leftover pie for breakfast and shimmy on over to bettyturbo dot com to grab one of these jerseys, ok?
Givin this one another whirl bc I was super unstoked on the color shift in the previous image. ✨ Hope you love it even more now! ✨ Please bask in its golden goodness.

Peppermint ornaments have been replenished! Bettyturbo dot com for a limited time til I pull everything for my holiday markets! They all have both faces so please be prepared to love them in all their moods, it’s an emotional time of year okayyy?

It’s my birthday! I’m older than Kenny Omega but younger than Chris Jericho. It’s been quite a year. I was going to summarize the amount of traveling and tattoos and wrestling but my brain is nothing but papier-mâché mush right now so there ya go. Joyeux blah blah blah.

One last batch of papier-mâché ornaments are available for you now! I’m pulling all inventory on Tuesday to pack for my holiday markets! We got new keytars, pop tarts, and celery, and a restock on shrimp! Have a snack at bettyturbo dot com why dontcha.

Let’s rock! Jam on these keytar ornaments today, coz tomorrow I’ll be taking all ornaments and shirts out of my shop to prep for holiday markets!

If you’re near Portland, catch me at @craftywonderland holiday sale at the convention center the 8th through the 10th, and then @mallratspdx art market at Lloyd Center on the 16th!

Hey all you neon nerds and blacklight gremlins of Nashville, we are happy to say you can check out one of our giant screenprints in “Everywhere is Beauty” at @haleygallerynashville, opening reception this Thursday! 🌷And for bonus floral fun, @gifthorsenashville is carrying some of our smaller flower studies! 🌼 Go lay yer peepers on em and let us know what you think! 🌸 Find the rest of this series online at bettyturbo dot com 🌺

My dear @blk.rnbw is continuing the time-honored Camp Corndog tradition of printing new items for Crafty at the very last minute! Last year it was these tote bags. (Still available!) Any guesses which Betty Turbo product is getting a tee shirt now?? 👀
You’re hot.

We are proud to announce the birth of this year’s Last Minute Print Job. Weighing in at 8oz of smooth ringspun cotton and infused with all the comfort food and b00b jokes you expect from Betty Turbo, this tee is a perfect snack for a rainy day. Grab one this weekend at the @craftywonderland holiday sale or online right this minute from bettyturbo dot com. 🍜 いただきます!

Ornament and shirt inventory has been added back to bettyturbo dot com for your shopping pleasure! I can’t offer any guarantees for holiday delivery but I will keep shippin every day! Oh and ✨surprise✨ I found one deviled egg and one Tom Peterson ornament who ran away together to the bottom of a shirt tote, so those are listed too.

Meet me at the MALL!  @mallratspdx art market tomorrow at Lloyd Center Mall from 11 to 7.  The corndog of the holiday shopping season has been nibbled down to a nub, but here’s a chance to shop unique goodies from over 40 local artists, including a fresh batch of ornaments I made just for the occasion. We’ll be on the first floor in the hollow candy shell of an old Express store near the ice rink. Hitch a ride on the Zamboni and come get some rad art and gifts.
Things I liked in 2023: wrestling. Things I would like more of in 2024: wrestling.

🌈 YOUR FRIEND BETTY TURBO
